<header id="home" class="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Maëlle Mohr</p>
    <h1>Aspiring AI and Data Architect, <span>business-oriented</span></h1>
    <p class="bio">
      Computer science student in the Grande École program at Epitech Nancy, currently
      focused on data engineering and AI. My interest in data comes from hands-on
      experience building ETL pipelines and Power BI dashboards during two internships —
      not just theory. I care about turning messy, real-world data into something a
      business can actually act on.
    </p>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <span class="label">Next up</span>
      <p>
        Academic exchange at <strong>HoGent</strong>, Ghent (2026–2027) — followed by a
        part-time internship search, <strong>September 2027 – February 2028</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-linkedin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="#projects" class="link">Projects</a>
      <a href="/cv-en.pdf" download class="link link-primary">Download CV</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .header {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 span {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .bio {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .next-steps {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .next-steps .label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .next-steps p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .link {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  .link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .link-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .link-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    color: var(--bg);
  }
</style>
